HEADWORD: Bricklaying
<hw>Brick"lay`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The art of building with
bricks, or of uniting them by cement or mortar into various forms; the
act or occupation of laying bricks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

